v0.9
	* Adds examples in Ruby
	* Adds software components to execute and explore simulations using Python scripts
	* Removes classes using Swing view
	* Replaces the existing server with a better MVC architecture
	* Uses Spark 2.7.1
	* Similar2Logo has its own logo
	* Updates the documentation
	* Similar2Logo has a new home: https://github.com/gildasmorvan/similar2logo
	* Solves a bug that caused passive agents no to be added in the environment. 

v0.8
	* Corrects maven packaging process
	* Corrects a bug with the probes defined in predation and virus examples
	* Corrects a bug that caused Spark to crash on some platforms
	* Corrects a bug that caused examples using a custom GUI to crash when executed from Similar2Logo distribution
	* Uses standard unicode charset to display controls instead of glyphicons
	* Uses Bootstrap 3.3.7 and Dygraphs 2.0
	* Uses a homemade FastMath library to compute atan2
	* Improves the GUI
	* Updates the documentation

v0.7
	* Deprecates classes using Swing view
	* Parametrizes Mark class
	* Optimizes the reaction model
	* Optimizes the JSON Probe
	* Optimizes environment primitives
	* Optimizes the perception model
	* Externalizes web resources
	* Improves the GUI
	* Adds examples in Groovy
	* Replaces the existing web server by a more efficient one  based on Spark
	* Adds an ant colony example in java
	* Adds pheromone field drawing in web GUI
	* Adds pheromone field to JSON export
	* Uses the websocket protocol to push JSON data to the client
	* Modifies the API
	* Updates the documentation

v0.6
	* Adds Parameter annotation to simulation parameters
	* Adds a HTML5 GUI
	* Adds a JSON Probe to export grid state in HTML5 GUI
	* Adds Randomwalk and Passive decision models in lib
	* Adds following, passive, predation, randomwalk, segregation and virus examples
	* Fixes reaction to ChangePosition influence in LogoDefaultReactionModel
	* Fixes bogus Javadoc
	* Uses Similar 0.2.6

